---
title: Truffled Mushroom Flatbreads with Shallot and a Green Side Salad
description: We think this recipe might just be a little bit more special than most thanks to a decadent drizzle of truffle oil. If you’ve never had it before, truffle has an incredible umami richness and intoxicating aromatics—think of it as the most luxurious mushroom flavor you’ve ever tasted. Speaking of mushrooms, this flatbread has tender slices of baby portobellos. And on the side, you’ve got a lemony arugula salad for a bit of bright green freshness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/truffled-mushroom-flatbread-162b5245.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/truffled-mushroom-flatbread-5cf148a58b02f000105e2832-42106ba9.pdf
cuisine: North America
